            <h2>Welcome to Hacktoberfest 2024!</h2>
            <p>Hacktoberfest is an annual event that encourages participation in the open-source community. It's a great opportunity to contribute to projects, learn new skills, and connect with other developers.</p>
            <p>This year, we're excited to see a wide range of contributions from all over the world. Whether you're a seasoned developer or just starting out, there's a place for you in the open-source community.</p>
            <p>Here are some tips to get started:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Find a project that interests you.</li>
                <li>Read the contribution guidelines.</li>
                <li>Start with small issues to get familiar with the project.</li>
                <li>Don't be afraid to ask for help!</li>
            </ul>
